      "id": "WF-CONTRACT-RISK-01",
      "severity": "high",
      "classification": "observed legacy privacy mismatch; not an approved target guarantee",
      "evidence": "Teacher self-profile removes username and accessStatus but returns raw composed Group rows, including monthlyFee, while OpenAPI marks Group.monthlyFee Admin only",
      "treatment": "Must be resolved through Product and Security review before target parity acceptance; migration must not silently preserve or expand the exposure"
    },
