      "evidence": "All ten operations are listed but exact schemas and most failure responses are absent",
      "treatment": "Use this baseline for WF-PRE-06 and WF-PRE-13; reconcile OpenAPI before Module Readiness passes"
    },
    {
      "id": "WF-CONTRACT-RISK-03",
      "severity": "medium",
      "classification": "legacy implementation quirk",
      "evidence": "Delete Working Hour returns teacherName as empty string because the deleted row is mapped without the Teacher join",
